body_html: While I have previously contributed code to tensorflow, I am not an ongoing team member; I work for an unrelated company doing unrelated things, and my contributions to tensorflow have been trivial fixes to issues I noticed in my spare time. Please give the tensorflow team time to see this thread and work through the issue, and be aware that if you found me to ping, you probably also pinged other people who are not core team members.
